ZH: 我正在家里换窗帘。
EN: I'm changing the curtains at home.

ZH: 这个房间的窗帘颜色太暗了。
EN: The color of the curtains in this room is too dark.

ZH: 我喜欢用透明的窗帘让阳光进入房间。
EN: I like using transparent curtains to let sunlight in.

ZH: 她正在洗窗帘，所以没时间接电话。
EN: She's washing the curtains, so she doesn't have time to answer the phone.

ZH: 窗帘的材质很重要，可以决定整个房间的氛围。
EN: The material of the curtains is important and can determine the atmosphere of the entire room.

ZH: 我需要买一些新的窗帘挂钩。
EN: I need to buy some new curtain hooks.

ZH: 这些窗帘可以完全遮光。
EN: These curtains can block out all the light.

ZH: 窗帘上的花纹很漂亮，让房间更有特色。
EN: The patterns on the curtains are beautiful and make the room more unique.

ZH: 请将窗帘拉开一点，我想看看外面的风景。
EN: Please pull the curtains back a little so I can see the view outside.

ZH: 我觉得这条窗帘太长了，需要修剪一下。
EN: I think this curtain is too long and needs to be trimmed.

ZH: 窗帘上的纱网可以有效阻挡蚊虫进入房间。
EN: The mosquito net on the curtain can effectively prevent insects from entering the room.

ZH: 窗帘杆上的装饰很精美。
EN: The decorations on the curtain rod are very exquisite.

ZH: 窗帘让房间变得更温馨。
EN: Curtains make the room feel cozier.

ZH: 换了新窗帘后，房间的气氛变得更加舒适。
EN: After replacing the curtains, the atmosphere of the room became more comfortable.

ZH: 我喜欢用吊帘作为窗帘，它们更漂亮且方便。
EN: I like using valances as curtains, they are more beautiful and convenient.

ZH: 窗帘饰品可以给房间增添一些色彩。
EN: Curtain accessories can add some color to the room.

ZH: 这条窗帘的花纹和房间的家具很搭配。
EN: The pattern of this curtain matches well with the furniture in the room.

ZH: 窗帘是房间装饰的重要组成部分。
EN: Curtains are an important component of room decoration.

ZH: 我买了一套新的窗帘，想让房间焕然一新。
EN: I bought a new set of curtains to give the room a fresh look.

ZH: 我已经洗好窗帘了，现在只需等它们晾干。
EN: I have washed the curtains, now I just need to wait for them to dry.
